<div class="banner" style="background-color: #9787FD;">
  <div class="container-top">
    <h1 class="headline"><span data-controller="typed-js"></span></h1>
    <div class="center-container">
      <p class= "tag_line">Paws: discover the perfect pet match through our extensive network of trusted shelters.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="center-container">
      <%= image_tag "pets_comp2.png", alt: "", width:"100%", class: "top_image"%>
    </div>
    <div class="center-container">
      <%= link_to "SEE ALL", "/pets", class: "btn btn-flat" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container_home">

  <div class="home-content-wrap">
    <div class="lilac-card" style="background-color: #9787FD;">
      <div class="image-container">
        <%= image_tag "pets_comp3.png", alt: "" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2 class="subhead">About Us</h2>
      <p class="home-text">At Paws, our mission is to forge enduring bonds between pets in need and caring families throughout Europe. We recognize the significance of discovering an ideal companion, and our devoted team is committed to guiding you through the pet adoption process with ease and assurance.</p>
      <p class="home-text">Our platform links you to an extensive network of reputable shelters and pet owners, providing a diverse selection of carefully chosen pets that align with your preferences, lifestyle, and living space. We firmly believe that every pet is deserving of a loving and nurturing home.</p>
      <p class="home-text">As a trusted partner in your pet adoption journey, we strive to ensure a seamless experience by offering personalized support and a wealth of resources. Together, we can help make a difference in the lives of countless pets and families, creating a brighter future for all.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="banner" style="background-color: #9787FD;">
  <div class="search-bar-container">
    <div class="center-container">
      <%= image_tag "pets_comp8.png", alt: "", width:"100%", class: "search_image"%>
    </div>
    <h1 class="headline_search">Start Your Search Now</h1>
    <div class="center-container">
      <div class="card-search">
      <div class="search-bar">
        <form action="/pets" method="get" class="form-inline">
          <div class="form-group">
            <select name="location" id="location" class="form-select form-control border-radius input-lg">
              <option value="">Location</option>
              <option value="France">France</option>
              <option value="Germany">Germany</option>
              <option value="Poland">Poland</option>
              <option value="Hungary">Hungary</option>
              <option value="Latvia">Latvia</option>
              <option value="Romania">Romania</option>
              <option value="Slovenia">Slovenia</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <select name="species" id="species" class="form-select form-control border-radius input-lg">
              <option value="">Pet Type</option>
              <% @pet_types.each do |type| %>
              <option value= <%= type %> ><%= type.capitalize %></option>
              <% end %>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <select name="gender" id="gender" class="form-select form-control border-radius input-lg">
              <option value="">Gender</option>
              <option value="male">Male</option>
              <option value="female">Female</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="number" name="age" id="age" min="1" class="form-select form-control border-radius input-lg" placeholder="Age">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-home">Search</button>
          </div>
        </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Pets -->
<div class="container_home">
  <div class="home-content-no-margin">
    <div class="text-container mt-5">
      <h2 class="subhead">Our Pets</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="see-container">
      <p class="see_more">See More</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-pets-home">
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-4 g-4">
      <% @random_pets.each do |pet| %>
        <% if pet.photo.attached? %>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card pets-view-card">
              <div class="pets-view-card pet_image">
                <%= cl_image_tag pet.photo.key, width: 100, class: "pet_image" %>
              </div>
                <a href="<%= "/pets/#{pet.id}" %>" class="discover-more-link">
                  <div class="card-body pet-view-info">
                    <div class="w-50">
                      <h5 class="pets-card-header"><%= pet.name %></h5>
                      <h6 class="card-text white-text"> <%= pet.breed %></h6>
                      <h6 class="card-text white-text"> <%= pet.gender %> ¬∑ <%= pet.age %> years old</h6>
                    </div>
                  <div class="pet-details">
                    <h6 class="shelter-top right-align-text">Located at</h6>
                    <div class="shelter-container">
                      <div class="shelter-content">
                        <h5 class="shelter right-align-text"><%= pet.shelter.name %></h5>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  </div>
                </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Events -->
  <div class="home-content-wrap">
    <div class="lilac-card" style="background-color: #9787FD;">
      <div class="image-container mt-1">
        <%= image_tag "pets_comp7.png", alt: "", style: "width: 98%;" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2 class="subhead">Events</h2>
      <p class="home-text">Join us at our adoption events and take the first step towards creating a lifelong bond with your perfect pet match. Our heartwarming events showcase a diverse array of lovable pets from trusted shelters, making it easy for you to meet and interact with your potential new companion in a friendly and supportive environment. We believe that every pet deserves a loving and nurturing home, and our goal is to connect you with the perfect pet that aligns with your preferences and lifestyle.</p>
      <p class="home-text">We understand that finding the right pet can be a challenging and overwhelming process, which is why our adoption events are designed to make the experience as enjoyable and stress-free as possible. Our events are held regularly at various locations throughout Europe, and our team is dedicated to ensuring that each event is a fun and memorable experience for both you and the pets.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Map -->
  <div data-controller="map"
    id='map'
    data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>"
    data-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
    style='width: 100%; height: 300px;'>
  </div>
<!-- Shelters -->
  <div class="home-content-no-margin mt-4">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2 class="subhead">Shelters</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="see-container">
      <p class="see_more">See More</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-shelters-home">
  <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-4 g-4 mb-5">
  <% @shelters.sample(8).each do |shelter| %>
    <% if shelter.photo.attached? %>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card shelter-view-card">
          <div class="shelter-view-card shelter_image">
            <%= link_to(shelter) do %>
            <%= cl_image_tag shelter.photo.key, width: 100, class: "shelter_image" %>
            <% end %>
            <div class="card-body shelter-view-info">
              <div class="w-100">
                <h4 class="shelters-card-header"><%= shelter.name %></h4>
                <p class="card-text-white-text">üìç<%= shelter.address %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
